      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MIGHTY MISS (2) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 0.7 lengths (22.66) behind Best Dressed at Warragul. Likely to feature again. WHOPPI DEVERE (1) is having her first start around this track. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 6 lengths (24.23) at Bendigo. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Worth another chance. PAW ESTRELLA (5) has been in sparkling form, last time breaking from this same box to win a Grade 5 at Bendigo (23.79) and making it three straight wins. Should be in this for a long way. ZIPPING SIGRID (7) is new to this circuit but can play a major role.",
